IN RE A.W. 2018-1182 Supreme Court of Ohio. November 7, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

APPEALS ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW Appeal accepted on proposition of law No. I. O'Connor, C.J., would accept the appeal on all propositions of law.

French and DeGenaro, JJ., would also accept the appeal on proposition of law No. II.

Fischer, J., would also accept the appeal on proposition of law No. IV.

O'Donnell, Kennedy, and DeWine, JJ., dissent.
